---
description: Project rules for the ScaleMotions Astro marketing site
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- This is a production Astro source project, not a Webflow upload package.
- Preserve SEO metadata, schema, and accessible heading hierarchy on every page.
- Put reusable copy and business data in src/data.
- Put repeated UI in src/components.
- Keep global design decisions in src/styles/tokens.css and src/styles/global.css.
- Never hardcode local machine paths.
- Do not add fake form handlers. Forms must point to a real GoHighLevel, Formspree, Netlify, or Worker endpoint when wired.
- Do not reintroduce Cloudflare Worker server logic into the static Astro site.
- Run npm run build before finalizing edits.

